Comment: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:42.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Don't wanna die before we see our fire inside, so
Comment: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(We can fight!)
Comment: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:47.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}泥まみれのその表情が見据えてる先へ
Comment: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(We can fly!)
Comment: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:53.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}流れ落ちる汗が全て無駄に終わるとしても
Comment: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:57.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}戦うことだけは忘れはしないだろう
Comment: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつでも笑える強い君の
Comment: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}泣き顔は誰も知らないから
Comment: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:08.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}心のアザは消えないけど
Comment: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(Let's go!)
Comment: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(Get up, get up, get up!)
Comment: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}You always never gave up,
Comment: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}You never gave up
Comment: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そう nothing's too late
Comment: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうやってnever wake up,
Comment: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}You never wake up
Comment: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}夢見て行こうぜ
Comment: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:23.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつか嘆いてた笑えない世界は
Comment: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}どこまでも笑って
Comment: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:27.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうさ
Comment: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Get up, get up, get up!
Comment: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}駆け抜ければいい
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Comment: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:48.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}季節が　駆けてく　息を　きらして
Comment: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:55.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}必死に　ついてく　淡すぎる衝動
Comment: 0,0:21:56.41,0:22:02.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}気づけば　誰もが　顔を　変えてく
Comment: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:09.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}周りを　気にして　白を黒という
Comment: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:15.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}自分にウソはつきたくない
Comment: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:22.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}幸せの　形は　ひとつだけじゃないから
Comment: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:29.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}変わる強さより　変わらない強さ
Comment: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:36.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}心に手をあてて　自分自身を今　愛してあげよう
Comment: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:43.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}変わる強さより　変わらない強さ
Comment: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:50.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}誰かのためじゃなく　今、未来へと
